{"title":"歌唱工地工厂","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":12,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱工地工厂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工地工厂真正好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造出机器几十套。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笨重工具都丢掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"省人省力工效高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丢掉钝挖锄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铲土直着腰；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丢掉硬扁担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着车子跑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丢掉笨石硪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踩机器乐逍遥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载湖北日报）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1}